Welcome to TP4 - Fraction on Exercism's Python Track.
If you need help running the tests or submitting your code, check out `HELP.md`.

## Instructions

$$
\int_3^63xdx
$$

### Part 1 - Creation and conversion to string conversion

```python
> f = Fraction(1, 2)
> f.numerator
1
> f.denominator
2
> f
1/2
```

### Part 2 - Equal

```python
> Fraction(1, 2) == Fraction(1, 2)
True
```

### Part 3 - Creation with simplification

```python
> Fraction(2, 4)
2/4
> Fraction(-2, -4)
2/4
> Fraction(2, -4)
-2/4
```

### Part 4 - Multiplication

```python
> Fraction(1, 2) * Fraction(1, 4)
1/8
```

### Part 5 - All arithmetic operations

### You should add the tests

```python
> Fraction(1,2) + Fraction(1,4)
3/4
> Fraction(1,2) - Fraction(1,4)
1/4
> Fraction(1,2) * Fraction(1,4)
1/8
> Fraction(1,2) / Fraction(1,4)
2
```
